name: THE LIMINAL SPACE : GATE
description:
THE LIMINAL SPACE : GATE is part of an ongoing series of THE LIMINAL SPACE I have been developing for quite awhile. 

Liminal space exists when physical experience meets the internal dialogue. An ever evolving space for one to comprehend the present time and its embodiment in many forms. 

THE LIMINAL SPACE : GATE explores the different approach of portraying the unknown familiarity using illustration.
